.Sh NAME
.Nm inadyn
.Nd A small DDNS client to maintain your presence on the Internet.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm inadyn
.Bk
.Op Fl a, -alias Ar ALIAS[,HASH]
.Op Fl b, -background
.Op Fl d, -drop-privs Ar USER[:GROUP]
.Op Fl e, -exec Ar SCRIPT
.Op Fl f, -forced-update Ar SEC
